content.html: I am sad to hear about Ted Cruz’s kid self-harming. But I’m more sad about how Ted Cruz didn’t seem to give a shit about how many other people’s kids self-harm because he’s actively working to deny them health care. Those chickens have come home to roost.
content.value:
I am sad to hear about Ted Cruz’s kid self-harming.

But I’m more sad about how Ted Cruz didn’t seem to give a shit about how many other people’s kids self-harm because he’s actively working to deny them health care.

Those chickens have come home to roost.
